                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Is there a contract?</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted">No lock-in contracts! Premium is billed annually, but you can cancel at any time. Your premium features remain active until the end of your paid period.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">What payment methods are accepted?</h4>
